highlights.text: “I Think I Like You Better When You’re Gone” by Reneé Rapp is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs USA, up 25 spots at #41.
“Pelotero A La Bola” by 8Uno and Airam Paez has been on Viral Songs USA the longest, at 77 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs USA. “Golden” is the highest at #6.
“Confess Your Love” by Jiandro and ola.wav is the highest new entry on Viral Songs USA at #2.
